<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal Isu min a sangpen hi,
 Sietlei leh thangvan ah;
 Angel leh mihing in a ho,
 Nuoi zinmang in alau

[V2]
 Nielna dang ka nei ta puoh ie,
 Midang ka ngai ta puoi;
 Krista thih kei di'n a hun ie,
 Kei dingin tha A kiei.

[V3]
 2. Isu min gilo di'n ahi,
 Gilo dinga piek chu;
 A gitloh mawhpuok A lamang,
 Gawtmun Van A chansak.

[V4]
 3. A lopina thu chu genin,
 A Hukdam thu phuong ka;
 Ka sep ding ziehaw hi ahi,
 Belam No etsak hi.</lyrics>
<title>Min Chungnung Pen</title>
<hymn_number>99</hymn_number>
</song>